## 4. Connection States

### Local Node Status (Event 10)

| Code | Status | Meaning |
|------|--------|---------|
| 1 | Online | Direct connections available |
| 2 | RelayActive | Connected via relay only |
| 3 | Syncing | Engine initializing |
| 4 | Offline | No network connections |

### Per-Peer Connection Status (Event 8)

| Code | Status | Meaning |
|------|--------|---------|
| 0 | Direct P2P | Direct QUIC/TCP connection |
| 1 | Relay Active | Connected through RBN relay |
| 2 | Offline | No connection to this peer |

### Connection Status Format (Event 8)

```
[PeerId bytes]:[StatusCode byte]
```

Example: `12D3KooW...:0` = Direct P2P connection to this peer.

