## 5. Messaging Protocol

### Message Types

| Type | Transport | Direction | Description |
|------|-----------|-----------|-------------|
| `ChatMessage` | Request-Response | 1:1 | Individual text message |
| `GroupMessage` | Gossipsub | Group | Group text message |
| `Acknowledgement` | Request-Response | Both | Delivery/read receipt |
| `FileTransfer` | Request-Response | 1:1 | File transfer initiation |
| `FileChunk` | Request-Response | 1:1 | File data chunk |
| `FileChunkRequest` | Request-Response | 1:1 | Request missing chunk |
| `FileTransferComplete` | Request-Response | Both | Transfer verification |
| `MessageReaction` | Request-Response | Both | Emoji reaction |
| `EditMessage` | Request-Response | Both | Edit sent message |
| `DeleteMessage` | Request-Response | Both | Delete message |
| `SetRetention` | Request-Response | Both | Disappearing messages timer |
| `ProfileUpdate` | Request-Response | Both | Name/avatar/handle update |
| `DirectInviteRequest` | Request-Response | Both | Contact request |
| `DirectInviteAccept` | Request-Response | Both | Contact acceptance |
| `WebRtcNative` | Request-Response | Both | WebRTC SDP/ICE signaling |
| `HandleClaimRequest` | Request-Response | Both | Handle registration |
| `HandleClaimWitnessed` | Request-Response | Both | Handle verification |

### ChatMessage Flow

```
Sender                                    Receiver
  │                                          │
  │  1. Create ChatMessage                   │
  │  2. Store locally (is_me=true)           │
  │  3. Send via forward_to_mesh             │
  │─────────────────────────────────────────►│
  │                                          │  4. Store locally (is_me=false)
  │                                          │  5. Send Ack {status: 1} (Delivered)
  │◄─────────────────────────────────────────│
  │  6. Update status → ✓✓ (Delivered)      │
  │                                          │
  │         ... User opens chat ...          │
  │                                          │
  │                                          │  7. Send Ack {status: 2} (Read)
  │◄─────────────────────────────────────────│
  │  8. Update status → ✓✓ (Read)           │
```

### Message Storage

**Local Database (SQLite + SQLCipher):**

```sql
-- messages table
CREATE TABLE messages (
    peer_id TEXT NOT NULL,
    content TEXT NOT NULL,
    is_me BOOLEAN NOT NULL,
    timestamp TEXT NOT NULL,
    status INTEGER DEFAULT 1,  -- 0=Sent, 1=Delivered, 2=Read
    msg_id TEXT,
    reply_to_msg_id TEXT
);

-- Index for fast peer lookups
CREATE INDEX idx_messages_peer ON messages (peer_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_messages_msg_id ON messages (msg_id);
```

### Message Format (Wire)

```
[timestamp: 8 bytes BE][msg_id_len: 1 byte][msg_id][reply_to_len: 1 byte][reply_to][content]
```

