### Event Types

| Code | Event | Direction | Payload |
|------|-------|-----------|---------|
| 1 | Ping | Rust→Dart | Empty |
| 2 | Message Received | Rust→Dart | `[timestamp:8][msg_id_len:1][msg_id][reply_to_len:1][reply_to][content]` |
| 4 | Group Message (legacy) | Rust→Dart | `[timestamp:8][content]` |
| 5 | Media Frame | Rust→Dart | `[MediaFrameHeader][payload]` |
| 7 | E2EE Session Established | Rust→Dart | `[peer_id_len:1][peer_id]` |
| 8 | Peer Connection Status | Rust→Dart | `[peer_id]:[status_code]` |
| 9 | Economy Stats | Rust→Dart | JSON stats |
| 10 | Local Node Status | Rust→Dart | `[status_code]` |
| 11 | Anchor Mode | Rust→Dart | `[0=Disabled,1=Enabled]` |
| 12 | File Transfer Progress | Rust→Dart | JSON FileTransferProgress |
| 13 | Message Status Update | Rust→Dart | `[status][msg_id]` |
| 14 | Incoming Call Offer | Rust→Dart | `[peer_id]` |
| 15 | WebRTC Signal | Rust→Dart | `[peer_id_len:1][peer_id][json]` |
| 16 | Call Ended/Rejected | Rust→Dart | `[peer_id]` |
| 20 | Contact Added | Rust→Dart | Contact data |
| 21 | Group Message | Rust→Dart | `[group_id_len:1][group_id][sender_len:1][sender][reply_to_len:1][reply_to][content]` |
| 22 | Group Member Updated | Rust→Dart | Group data |
| 23 | Group Message (variant) | Rust→Dart | Same as 21 |
| 24 | Group Invite | Rust→Dart | `[inviter_id_len:1][inviter_id][group_name_len:1][group_name][group_id]` |
| 25 | Peer Profile Updated | Rust→Dart | `[pid_len:1][pid][name_len:1][name][handle_len:1][handle][avatar_len:4][avatar]` |
| 26 | Group Join Request | Rust→Dart | `[group_id\0requester_pid\0alias\0handle\0avatar]` |
| 27 | Group Join Rejected | Rust→Dart | `[group_id\0group_name\0reason]` |
| 30 | Swarm Stats | Rust→Dart | JSON stats |
| 31 | Connection Request | Rust→Dart | `[PID\0Name\0Handle\0Avatar]` |
| 32 | Connection Accepted | Rust→Dart | `[PID\0Name]` |
| 33 | Handle Resolved | Rust→Dart | `[Handle\0PID]` |
| 35 | Handle Resolve Failed | Rust→Dart | `[handle]` |
| 37 | Message Deleted | Rust→Dart | Deletion data |
| 38 | Message Edited | Rust→Dart | Edit data |
| 99 | Rust Debug Log | Rust→Dart | Debug text |

