| Relayed QUIC | **2 Mbps** | Cross-network via RBN |
| Relayed TCP | **1 Mbps** | UDP blocked, TCP fallback |
| Group Swarm (3 peers) | **40 Mbps** | Same LAN, 3 seeders |
| Group Swarm (8 peers) | **80 Mbps** | Same LAN, 8 seeders |

